election_record.label: Connecticut 1820 State Senate

overview.note: John S. Peters received 3 votes as John Peters and 1 vote as Jonathan S. Peters.
Andrew Hull received 59 votes as Andrew Hall and 1 vote as Andrew Hall.
William M. Betts received 1 vote as William H. Betts.
Charles H. Hall received 2 votes as Charles Hill, 2 votes as Charles L. Hall, 1 vote as Charles Hull, 1 vote as Charles W. Hall and 1 vote as Charles B. Hall.
Nathaniel Terry received 1 vote as Nathaniel Perry and 1 vote as Nathaniel Perry, Jr.
Ansel Sterling received 1 vote as Anson Sterling.
Elijah Boardman received 1 vote as Elisha Boardman.

sub_unit.name: Wethersfield
sub_unit.note: John S. Peters received 113 votes as J. H. Peters.

sub_unit.name: Saybrook
sub_unit.note: There were no votes recorded in Saybrook.
